            "pathId": -7442831419503049005,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "おっと、そりゃ大変だ。\nんー、どーしたもんか……。",
            "enText": "Oh, that seems intense. <i>Hmmm</i>, \nwhaaat to do now then…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 818409166900358079
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -4821980086752179223
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3513440177598766981,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ま、慌ててもしょうがない。\nしばらく散歩でもするか。",
            "enText": "Well, no need to be anxious. \nGuess I'll go for a stroll then.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": 3206525186003747003
