            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "にしても、\n適当な駅で降りるのっていいよな～。",
            "enText": "Even so, this is a great station to \nbe getting off at～",
